bleTag\">Hiking <br />\n</span></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"htmlTag\"><span class=\"tableTag\">Kayaks/canoes (requires sign-up)</span></span></li>\n<li><span class=\"htmlTag\"><span class=\"tableTag\">Skeet shooting (requires $)&nbsp;</span></span> </li>\n<li>Darts, pool, shuffleboard</li>\n<li>Lounging</li></ul></td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td>\n<div><strong>7:30pm</strong></div></td>\n<td>\n<div>Dinner&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (Dining Hall)</div></td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td>\n<div><strong>8pm</strong></div></td>\n<td>\n<div>Musical performance by Dimitri and Alice &nbsp; (Dining Hall)</div></td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td>\n<div><strong>9pm - 2am</strong></div></td>\n<td>\n<div>DJ with dance music &nbsp; (Dining Hall)</div></td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td>\n<div>&nbsp;</div></td>\n<td>\n<div>&nbsp;</div></td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td colspan=\"2\">\n<div>\n<h2>&nbsp;Sunday, May 1st </h2></div></td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td>\n<div><strong>8am - 10am </strong></div></td>\n<td>\n<div>Continental Breakfast&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (Main Lodge)</div></td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td>\n<div><strong>9am - 12pm</strong></div></td>\n<td>\n<div>Check-out &nbsp;&nbsp; (Office) </div></td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\">\n<td>\n<div><strong>9am - 2pm&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\n</strong></div></td>\n<td>\n<div>Airport shuttles leave</div></td></tr></tbody></table></p>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n<hr style=\"width: 50%\" align=\"left\" />\n<h2>Activity Sign-up:</h2></div>\n<div>(coming soon)</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>', null, null, null, null, null, null, '1', '', '', '', '', null, null, '', '', '', '', null, null, null, null, '1293412217', null, '');
REPLACE INTO `rvs_project_page` (`project_page_id`, `rvs_usr_id`, `page_name`, `custom_page_name`, `rvs_component_id`, `page_data`, `page_data_zone_2`, `page_data_zone_3`, `page_data_zone_4`, `colume_width_1`, `colume_width_2`, `colume_width_3`, `rvs_layout_id`, `head`, `page_title`, `meta_keyword`, `meta_description`, `effect_page_enter`, `duration_page_enter`, `meta_page_effect`, `rvs_link_id`, `target`, `form_template_id`, `i_pathway`, `i_mail`, `i_print`, `i_favorite`, `last_modifier`, `link_active`, `page_type`) VALUES ('ac7e6a6825fb4a0c62884ae048d8dc73', 'c6cfcbb6a5d54aa5f85a869579e0989f', 'Accommodations', '', '0', '<div align=\"center\">\n<div align=\"center\"><font style=\"font-size: 24px\">Moon River Ranch</font></div>\n<div align=\"center\"><font style=\"font-size: 24px\"><strong>On-site Accommodations</strong> </font><br />\n</div>\n<div align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div></div>\n<div align=\"center\">\n<div align=\"center\"><img alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"/3rdparty/rvsitebuilder/project/8c4ecb967d961441575fd98192e10d28/documents/venue/photos_family_reunions_lake.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"346\" /></div></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div align=\"center\">Hopefully you\'ll consider staying on the ranch with us!&nbsp; Not only will you be near the excitement and the cool wedding people, you\'ll also get all of the luxuries of this fantastic, rustic, relaxing resort.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div align=\"center\">Below the pictures is a reservation form where you can reserve, and put a down payment on, a room. </div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div align=\"center\"><img alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"/3rdparty/rvsitebuilder/project/8c4ecb967d961441575fd98192e10d28/documents/venue/photos_corporate_retreats_barn_outside.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" />&nbsp;</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div align=\"center\"><img alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"/3rdparty/rvsitebuilder/project/8c4ecb967d961441575fd98192e10d28/documents/venue/photos_private_vacations_cabin_inside_2.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"346\" /></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div align=\"center\"><img alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"/3rdparty/rvsitebuilder/project/8c4ecb967d961441575fd98192e10d28/documents/venue/photos_family_reunions_front_porch.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"345\" /></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div align=\"center\"><img alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"/3rdparty/rvsitebuilder/project/8c4ecb967d961441575fd98192e10d28/documents/venue/photos_family_reunions_pool_evening.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"359\" /></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>Below is the Reservation form if you would like to purchase a room, bunk, or Airstream on the ranch.&nbsp; You can choose to have the accommodation for one night, or two. </div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n<div>Exact room location will be assigned at the wedding.&nbsp; A full payment can be made now, or you can make a down payment of half, with the other half due at the event.</div></div>\n<div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div>\n<div>All credit card purchases are through a secure site on PayPal.&nbsp; They will go directly to Dimitri and Alice, who will pay the venue.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>To begin, please select your name from the list.</div>\n<p>\n<div>\nIf your name is not in this list then<u> <a href=\"9549b5dc8c010729dbf7c8e7e0c4b6cf.php\" title=\"\">RSVP here</a></u>, first.</div><br />\n<form action=\"http://dimitriandalice.com/scripts/accommSQL.php\" method=\"post\"><?php 	\n	$linkID = @mysql_connect( \"localhost\", \"dimitria_web\", \"wedding\" ) \n			  or die( \"Error opening database: \" . mysql_error() . \". please try again.  \");\n	mysql_select_db(\"dimitria_wedding\", $linkID );\n	\n	print \"<select name=\"guest_name\">\";\n	$result = mysql_query( \"SELECT last_name, first_name, guest_id FROM rsvps WHERE attendance = \'yes\'\", $linkID );\n	while ( $row = mysql_fetch_row( $result ) ) \n	{\n		print \"<option value=\"$row[2]\">$row[0], $row[1]</option>\";\n	}\n	print \"</select>\";\n	\n	mysql_close( $linkID );?></form>\n<div>\n<div><br />\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>Other accommodations:</div>\n<div>Marlin, TX (12 miles)</div>\n<div>&nbsp;- Budget Inn</div>\n<div>&nbsp;- Relax Inn</div>\n<div>&nbsp;- Marlin Inn</div></div>\n<div>\n<div>&nbsp;- Best Western</div></div></div>\n<div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div>\n<div>Waco, TX (16 miles)</div>\n<div>&nbsp;- Super 8</div>\n<div>&nbsp;- Sleep Inn &amp; Suites</div>\n<div>&nbsp;- Fairfield Inn</div>\n<div>&nbsp;- Hampton Inn</div>\n<div>&nbsp;- Hometown Suites (Hilton)</div></div></div></div></p>', null, null, null, null, null, null, '1', '', '', '', '', null, null, '', '', '', '', null, null, null, null, '1292574846', null, '');
REPLACE INTO `rvs_project_page` (`project_page_id`, `rvs_usr_id`, `page_name`, `custom_page_name`, `rvs_component_id`, `page_data`, `page_data_zone_2`, `page_data_zone_3`, `page_data_zone_4`, `colume_width_1`, `colume_width_2`, `colume_width_3`, `rvs_layout_id`, `head`, `page_title`, `meta_keyword`, `meta_description`, `effect_page_enter`, `duration_page_enter`, `meta_page_effect`, `rvs_link_id`, `target`, `form_template_id`, `i_pathway`, `i_mail`, `i_print`, `i_favorite`, `last_modifier`, `link_active`, `page_type`) VALUES ('2e6e09d62cf110267af3f76e146ba8c2', 'c6cfcbb6a5d54aa5f85a869579e0989f', 'Travel', '', '0', '<div>\n<div>\n<h2>Suggested flight dates:</h2></div></div>\n<div>\n<div>4/29/10 (Friday)</div>\n<div>&nbsp;5/1/10 (Sunday)</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n<h2>Suggested airports:</h2> </div>\n<div>Austin, TX -<strong> AUS</strong>&nbsp; (112 miles)</div>\n<div>Waco, TX - <strong>ACT </strong>(24 miles) </div>\n<div>Dallas-Ft. Worth, TX -<strong> DFW</strong> (129 miles)</div></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<h2>Free Airport Shuttles&nbsp;</h2>\n<div>&nbsp;We will have voluntary drivers leaving/arriving at the two major airports at the following times.&nbsp; I will send out an email when the sign-up system is available.&nbsp; Until then, feel free to schedule your flights around these times.&nbsp;</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div>\n<div><strong>Austin </strong></div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li>Friday - leave airport at 4pm&nbsp;&nbsp; (sign-up coming soon)<br />\n</li>\n<li>Sunday - arrive at airport at 11am&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (sign-up coming soon)<br />\n</li></ul></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<div><strong>Dallas</strong></div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li>Friday - leave airport at 4pm&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (sign-up coming soon)</li>\n<li>Sunday - arrive at airport at 11am&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (sign-up coming soon)</li></ul></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<h2>Car Pools</h2></div>\n<div>\n<div>If you cannot schedule your flights around the above times, or are a local resident to Austin or Dallas that would like to carpool, then the below sign-up system will also be made available to connect people.&nbsp; I will send an email when this system is ready to use, so keep an eye out!</div></div>\n<div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div>\n<div>(car-pool sign-up system coming soon)<br />\n<div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div></div></div></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div>\n<div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div></div>\n<div>\n<div>Any further questions: <a href=\"&#109;&#97;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;&#58;&#68;&#105;&#109;&#105;&#116;&#114;&#105;&#64;&#68;&#105;&#109;&#105;&#116;&#114;&#105;&#65;&#110;&#100;&#65;&#108;&#105;&#99;&#101;&#46;&#99;&#111;&#109;\" title=\"\">&#68;&#105;&#109;&#105;&#116;&#114;&#105;&#64;&#68;&#105;&#109;&#105;&#116;&#114;&#105;&#65;&#110;&#100;&#65;&#108;&#105;&#99;&#101;&#46;&#99;&#111;&#109;</a><br />\n</div></div>', null, null, null, null, null, null, '1', '', '', '', '', null, null, '', '', '', '', null, null, null, null, '1293414362', null, '');
